The first issue is that the styling is attached to the head so is inaccessible to the ShadowRoot

Though this can be addressed with a slightly hacky method to copy the styles by adding 
```js
 useEffect(() => {
    // Detect and Move Styles to Shadow DOM:
    const shadowHost = document.querySelector('#excalidraw-shadow-host') as HTMLElement;
    if(shadowHost) {
      const shadowRoot = shadowHost.shadowRoot as ShadowRoot;
      const excalidrawStyles = document.querySelectorAll('style[data-source="excalidraw"]');
      // Copy each style tag into the shadow DOM
      excalidrawStyles.forEach(style => {
        shadowRoot.appendChild(style.cloneNode(true));
      });
    }
  }, []);
